data.title: Chantoozies kiss n tell
data.meta_description: The Australian Securities and Investments Commission received has received some terrifying correspondence: the registration of a new company, The Chantoozies Pty Ltd. Its directors are listed as the ‘80’s pop group’s singers Ally Fowler, Tottie Goldsmith, Eve Von Bibra and Angelica Arnott (formerly La Bozzetta).
data.text:
The Australian Securities and Investments Commission has received some terrifying correspondence: the registration of a new company, The Chantoozies Pty Ltd. Its directors are listed as the ‘80s’ pop group’s singers Ally Fowler, Tottie Goldsmith , Eve Von Bibra and Angelica Arnott (formerly La Bozzetta).

Given they’ve just released their first single in 23 years, could this be the beginning of a sustained comeback attempt? Or just somewhere to stash the box office takings?
